568
00:33:41.553 --> 00:33:42.754
Let me try.

569
00:33:42.888 --> 00:33:45.224
That kind of thing might take centuries to crack.

570
00:33:45.891 --> 00:33:47.093
Give me a week.

571
00:33:51.130 --> 00:33:52.698
A week. that's all I ask.

572
00:33:53.165 --> 00:33:55.201
I hate goats.

573
