You know. they pair goats with. uh. thoroughbreds.

574
00:34:01.840 --> 00:34:04.343
They call them companion animals.

575
00:34:05.244 --> 00:34:07.379
You see. horses don't like to be left on their own.

576
00:34:07.513 --> 00:34:09.081
They're herd animals. and they. uh.

577
00:34:09.215 --> 00:34:10.382
well. they get very lonely.

578
00:34:10.516 --> 00:34:15.121
So the breeders will put a goat in the horse pen

579
00:34:15.254 --> 00:34:18.224
to keep it settled and manageable and docile.

580
00:34:18.357 --> 00:34:22.461
But the. uh. the entire dynamic is...

581
00:34:23.262 --> 00:34:24.663
is very unnatural.

582
00:34:24.796 --> 00:34:27.433
First. you've taken a horse out of its natural environment.

583
00:34:27.566 --> 00:34:29.601
and then you paper over this perversion

584
00:34:29.735 --> 00:34:31.970
by forcing a companion on it.

585
00:34:32.104 --> 00:34:33.439
But some horses

586
00:34:35.274 --> 00:34:36.375
are different.

587
00:34:36.508 --> 00:34:37.609
They prefer solitude.

588
00:34:37.743 --> 00:34:42.214
and they see the goat as an intruder.

589
00:34:43.415 --> 00:34:44.750
An invader.

590
00:34:45.551 --> 00:34:47.486
And so they'll do what any animal would do

591
00:34:47.619 --> 00:34:49.054
when it feels threatened.

592
00:34:49.955 --> 00:34:50.989
I mean.

593
00:34:53.058 --> 00:34:55.227
horses don't even eat meat.

594
00:34:56.027 --> 00:34:59.931
But they will chew clean through a goat's neck.

595
00:35:02.434 --> 00:35:03.602
Imagine that.

596
00:35:05.637 --> 00:35:07.273
And you know what the owner does?

597
00:35:09.708 --> 00:35:10.842
Just buy us another goat.

598
00:35:10.976 --> 00:35:12.387
All right. I think that's fucking enough.

599
00:35:12.411 --> 00:35:13.679
We're not waiting!

600
00:35:15.881 --> 00:35:18.250
Not a week! Not a day!

601
00:35:18.584 --> 00:35:20.319
You fix my hardware.

602
00:35:20.452 --> 00:35:22.521
You fix my software.

603
00:35:22.654 --> 00:35:25.157
My schedule. or I'm done!

604
00:35:30.629 --> 00:35:33.599
It's not the first time that
he's threatened to take his ball

605
00:35:33.732 --> 00:35:34.732
and go home.

606
00:35:34.833 --> 00:35:36.235
He's an unstable man.

607
00:35:36.368 --> 00:35:38.580
Yeah. well. it's all we can do
to keep him together with meds

608
00:35:38.604 --> 00:35:39.671
and duct tape.

609
00:35:42.073 --> 00:35:45.544
So I guess you realize the other reason you're both here.

610
00:35:46.111 --> 00:35:48.680
The moment that Perry is not functional.

611
00:35:52.017 --> 00:35:53.519
We get it.

612
00:35:53.819 --> 00:35:55.221
We're the replacements.

613
00:36:00.326 --> 00:36:04.363
So I will get you your week. Annika.

614
00:36:05.331 --> 00:36:08.600
And I will smooth things over with Perry tomorrow.

615
00:36:09.034 --> 00:36:10.236
All right?

616
