699
00:41:50.475 --> 00:41:52.243
But they simply mimic those more developed.

700
00:41:52.377 --> 00:41:53.855
- But the-
- Does the parent have any idea

701
00:41:53.879 --> 00:41:54.880
what the child means?

702
00:41:55.013 --> 00:41:56.733
No. but they know what the child is saying.

703
00:41:57.816 --> 00:42:00.752
They're saying. "I'm alive and I'm listening."

704
00:42:04.289 --> 00:42:08.259
Yet though we babble. we do so mathematically.

705
00:42:08.393 --> 00:42:11.663
We will use two universal constants.

706
00:42:11.797 --> 00:42:14.666
The speed of light will be the unit of measurement.

707
00:42:15.200 --> 00:42:16.201
And primes.

708
00:42:16.334 --> 00:42:18.036
we will repeat the code ten times.

709
00:42:18.169 --> 00:42:20.672
The first interval will be two times the speed of light.

710
00:42:20.806 --> 00:42:22.207
And the final interval. therefore.

711
00:42:22.340 --> 00:42:25.911
will be the tenth prime 29 times the speed of light.

712
00:42:27.545 --> 00:42:29.781
You're saying a lot more than just hello.

713
00:42:29.915 --> 00:42:31.149
Yes.

714
00:42:31.282 --> 00:42:33.551
We're saying. "We've heard you and we're logical."

715
00:42:34.753 --> 00:42:36.287
And. "We're here."

716
00:42:37.555 --> 00:42:38.890
Yes. that's the idea.

717
00:42:41.059 --> 00:42:43.394
By the way. Sam won't stop it.

718
00:42:44.362 --> 00:42:45.430
There's no kill switch.

719
00:42:45.563 --> 00:42:47.265
And even if he could. he never would.

720
00:42:47.398 --> 00:42:51.136
He's blinded by hubris in one eye and glory in the other.

721
00:42:52.838 --> 00:42:55.440
Anything else from the little goats?

722
00:43:02.347 --> 00:43:03.548
Yeah.

723
