Like a quote for posterity or something.

729
00:43:15.460 --> 00:43:17.162
What. like. "One small step"?

730
00:43:17.295 --> 00:43:19.931
Or. "I am become Death. destroyer of worlds"?

731
00:43:20.298 --> 00:43:21.566
I mean. something.

732
00:43:21.700 --> 00:43:23.344
Considering what's about to happen. It's...

733
