There's no grand enlightenment.

737
00:43:35.313 --> 00:43:36.848
Just a thundering silence.

738
00:43:39.651 --> 00:43:41.186
This is about insignificance.

739
00:43:41.319 --> 00:43:44.289
This is about our smallness laid bare.

740
00:43:44.422 --> 00:43:49.961
There'll be no response because we simply do not matter.

741
00:43:50.095 --> 00:43:52.798
Not our work. not our deeds.

742
00:43:52.931 --> 00:43:55.166
Or our mistakes.

743
00:43:56.634 --> 00:43:58.003
So there's your fucking quote.

744
00:43:59.570 --> 00:44:01.639
