So. when's it happening?

750
00:44:40.278 --> 00:44:41.312
Five minutes ago.

751
00:44:41.446 --> 00:44:42.814
Really? And?

752
00:44:42.948 --> 00:44:44.249
And I'm done!

753
00:44:44.382 --> 00:44:46.651
Whoa. Annika. uh. look. don't...

