System offline.

759
00:45:32.097 --> 00:45:34.699
Uh. Perry. Perry. you should shut it off.

760
00:45:34.833 --> 00:45:36.267
Perry. shut-shut it off!

761
00:45:36.401 --> 00:45:37.435
- Shut it down!
- Shh!

762
