Annika. I got it.

763
00:46:03.594 --> 00:46:05.496
Why'd you turn it on. Charlie?

764
00:46:05.630 --> 00:46:06.630
Just hold on a sec.

765
00:46:09.600 --> 00:46:11.169
You need to come see this.

766
