777
00:46:38.696 --> 00:46:40.531
We at NASA. we're at a loss.

778
00:46:40.665 --> 00:46:43.268
Whatever it is. it extends beyond the Earth's atmosphere

779
00:46:43.401 --> 00:46:46.337
